originalText.text: We recently collaborated with Push Analytics for an integration project between HubSpot and NetSuite, and I must say, their performance was exceptional. Push Analytics completed the task in half the time compared to our previous vendor, and notably, at half the cost, which was impressive. This efficient integration has significantly streamlined our financial processes, making data management between HubSpot and NetSuite seamless and more effective. Their team demonstrated profound expertise and a commitment to understanding our specific needs, resulting in a tailor-made solution that exceeded our expectations. Their swift delivery and cost-effectiveness without compromising on quality make Push Analytics a highly recommendable partner for similar integration needs.

originalText.text:
HubSpot is a great CRM for both sales and marketing teams. Unfortunately, it is not an out-of-the-box solution for all business models and requires customization to optimize the platform for each business’s unique use case. My company, like many others, has a unique business model that does not conform to the basic features and fields of HubSpot. Searching for a resource to help get our account stood up correctly, we found Moustafa and his team at Push Analytics.

Although we are still in the process of implementation and training, we have been working with Moustafa for some time now. Him and his team are very knowledgeable about all things HubSpot, and are very helpful with configuration, customization, and training of HubSpot tools for both the Marketing and Sales side. He and his team never fail to provide answers to our questions and solutions for our concerns. They are quick, professional, and provide expertise in HubSpot features that can seem overwhelming to a new or moderate user of the platform. I thoroughly enjoy working with the Push Analytics team, and would highly recommend them to any business looking to take their HubSpot account, team productivity, and marketing and sales to the next level!

They provide us with industry specific content angles each month and an in-depth report of our previous months’ success and opportunities.  They are the perfect fit for our team's growing needs.
